<h3 id='field-width'>Field : width()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">field_width</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">field</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">width</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>This returns the <strong>width</strong> of the current battlefield in s (including <em>hidden</em> tiles).</p>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>field:width()</code></p>
<h4 id='return-value'>Return Value</h4>
<p><strong><code>integer</code></strong></p>
